{
  "texts": [
    "In the context of this study on social network anonymization, the alluvial diagram demonstrates how the authors' keywords have changed over time and how they relate to each other.",
    "The diagram consists of a series of vertical bars or columns, each representing one of the four subperiods that was defined previously.",
    "The columns are connected by horizontal lines, and the width of the lines represents the number of keywords that are shared between adjacent subperiods.",
    "The PageRank score of each keyword is calculated in each block, demonstrating the importance of nodes (keywords) within the network.",
    "(All the keywords in each module, along with their PageRank scores, are presented in Appendix C.) By analyzing the PageRank scores of the keywords within each block, we gained insight into the most influential themes and concepts in the social network anonymization field, as well as an understanding the relationships and connections between these themes."
  ]
}